Product name: SALE! Obsidian Black Bath Bomb, handmade bath bombs, custom made to order,black bath, Softens skin (many sizes)
Description:
FREE SHIPPING! USE CODE FREESHIP50 FOR ORDERS OVER 50.00
Our Obsidian Black bath bombs will dissolve and transform your water into a dark and luxurious pool to soak away all of your stress and worry from the day with just the right balance of  oils and fragrance. Remember the bigger the bomb, the darker the water! Available in many sizes and scents, please read below.
NEW FRAGRANCES ADDED!!! Country Apply, sweet cinnamon pumpkin, juicy strawberry, cinnamon roll, blueberry tea and a much more fragrant lemon essential!
SCENT OPTIONS:
Blackberry Vanilla, Grapefruit, Jasmine, Lemon, Peppermint, Rose, Sweet Orange, Tea Tree, Vanilla, Unscented and Love Spell (fusion of citrus, cherry blossom, hydrangea, apple and peach for an amazing smell)
OTHER INFO PLEASE READ!
*Please note that any deeply pigmented product has the potential to stick to residue in your tub or on your skin.  A VERY CLEAN TUB IS RECOMMENDED BEFORE USING ANY BATH COLORANTS, IT IS ALSO RECOMMENDED TO SHOWER WITH SOAP AFTER TO REMOVE ANY ADDITIONAL RESIDUE IF NEEDED.  Older tubs may experience discoloration over time due to their porous nature. Any product residue not removed by water can be cleaned using dish soap (my favorite) or other cleaner depending on what type of tub you have.
*Please also understand that because these bath bombs are handmade, and the size of your tub may vary compared to someone else's, the color of your bath water may vary from person to person. We try our best to make the best shades possible, but because of these differences there will be variations. Be wary about adding too many bath bombs at once, which can over concentrate your water color and lead to staining.
To make sure you get the best quality during use, make sure to keep your bath bombs in a dry cool place out of direct sunlight. A wet environment can lead to a decrease in the fizz by causing an early reaction, and too much sunlight can fade the beautiful colors in the bath bombs.
SHIPPING AND RETURNS
Products are carefully shipped from Rochester, NY within the domestic United States only.
We can not accept returns due to the fragile nature of our products. Please feel free to contact us if there is any damage to the product and we will do our best to make things right. 
Tracking information will be provided in an Etsy message once the order is shipped.

Product name: 5 Flux Brushes for Flux, Soldering Supply, Stained Glass Supply, Soldered Jewelry and Soldered Art Supply, Pendants
Description:
5 Flux Brushes for Flux, Soldering Supply, Stained Glass Supply, Soldered Jewelry and Soldered Art Supply, Pendants
5 Flux Brushes for applying flux.
Please don't leave your brush in the flux while you are working as it gets too much flux on the brush and this is one way of getting too much flux on your piece!
If, when you solder, your pieces hisses or sizzles...that is your piece 'telling you' that you have applied too much flux. Too much flux and your solder line won't be as smooth.
You can use these for patina but we much prefer to us cotton balls so we can rub the patina into the piece.

Description:
A 10-metre (11 yards) length of recycled sari silk ribbon handdyed in the pretty Buddleia colourway of pale pinks and lilacs.
The ribbon is a by-product from the manufacture of sari silk; the strips of fabric are tied or sewn together by women's cooperatives in India. I have handdyed these ribbon yarns in various colourways here in Cornwall, England. 
Due to the handmade and handdyed nature of the ribbon yarn each pack may differ, and will contain raw edges, knots and seams, and varying widths of ribbon (approx 3mm to 30mm if ironed flat) along its length.
